{"tid":923097,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿拉斯加7級地震建築物現裂痕 一段公路「完全消失」","createTime":"2018-12-01T03:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T09:00:47.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6b79f5bd27b0865d379014256d3103db0df37404","tid":923097,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"美國阿拉斯加州安克雷奇(Anchorage)發生7級地震，多幢建築物及基建設施嚴重受損，Ted Stevens國際機場一度關閉，鐵路暫停行駛，多條公路嚴重斷裂甚至有一部份「完全消失」。州長宣佈當地進入災難狀態。<br />\n地震發生在當地周五早上8時29分，震央位於安克雷奇以北12公里，震源深度40公里。地震發生時，市內建築物、燈柱和樹木搖動，商業大廈內的人慌忙走到街上或蹲到辦公桌下躲避。美聯社記者見到市中心一幢兩層高建築物有裂痕，安克雷奇機場附近一段斜坡塌陷，又有多輛汽車撞在一起。電力服務受影響，交通燈失靈。有數人輕傷，多數是被玻璃碎割到或被掉下的東西砸傷。<br />\n相關新聞：【阿拉斯加地震】近萬戶停電 居民：37年來最強烈<br />\n<br />\n地震令機場所有航班一度暫停升降數小時，控制塔人員亦要疏散。長1287公里的阿拉斯加油管亦一度關閉，當局派出工作人員前往檢查油管有否受損。<br />\n在帕默(Palmer)一間學校餐廳工作的貝利(Sheila Bailey)說︰「我們互相扶著，你甚至無法站立，就像學校要斷開兩截了。」安克雷奇學校宣佈停課，要求家長到學校接回子女。<br />\n地震後當局向阿拉斯加南部沿岸地區發出海嘯警告，阿拉斯加科迪亞克島(Kodiak island)警方呼籲島上居民到高處暫避，擔心會有巨浪湧至，幸而短時間後取消海嘯警告。在地震停止後，不少人返回建築物內，但不久後又發生強度達5.7級餘震，他們又再匆匆走回街上。<br />\n警方表示，安克雷奇東北方風光明媚的Glenn公路，有一部份「完全消失」。這段路會途經農田、高山和冰川。<br />\n阿拉斯加州長沃克(Bill Walker)在Twitter表示，他已頒佈該州進入災難狀態。而正在阿根廷出席20國集團峯會的總統特朗普，已聽取災情滙報，並密切留意地震最新的破壞報告。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181201/large/1543626341_c479.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181201%2Flarge%2F1543626341_c479.jpg&h=74d1c247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181201/large/1543626341_9d9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181201%2Flarge%2F1543626341_9d9a.jpg&h=19d5f24e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181201/large/1543602907_0960.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181201%2Flarge%2F1543602907_0960.jpg&h=b60c0c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181201/large/1543603498_732c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181201%2Flarge%2F1543603498_732c.jpg&h=d510e5a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181201/58979021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181201%2F58979021&d=1puHGPAGbSmSENI0cD9hRgKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=15d8477b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181201%2F58979021&h=2e405c06\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181201/58979021</a>"},{"pid":"2bd712ad035af7a1efe2661303d975b0358a334c","tid":923097,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:26:45.000Z","msg":"早兩日係新蛋買野件貨曾經停留係Anchorage個FedEx hub成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13330d74abfdae9e1dadec66f5a89c5a2c32826","tid":923097,"uid":47674,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2bd712ad035af7a1efe2661303d975b0358a334c","tid":923097,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:26:45.000Z","msg":"早兩日係新蛋買野件貨曾經停留係Anchorage個FedEx hub成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:35:23.000Z","msg":"您的快件已被震毀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457c6be3025d0621c5f9fdc1fd3dc04cee14839f","tid":923097,"uid":31946,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a13330d74abfdae9e1dadec66f5a89c5a2c32826","tid":923097,"uid":47674,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2bd712ad035af7a1efe2661303d975b0358a334c","tid":923097,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T03:26:45.000Z","msg":"早兩日係新蛋買野件貨曾經停留係Anchorage個FedEx h